This non-interventional, multi-centric, cross-sectional study is aimed to determine the prevalence of Chronic Kidney Disease in Indian patients with Type 2 Diabetes (T2DM).

 3000 patients will be enrolled from 30 investigative sites all over the country.

 Each investigative site will be expected to enrol 100 subjects.

 All the procedures will be completed in a single day.

